-- slice 10: a C-constructed None (IMMEDIATE reserved tag) hits the None arm.
-- 55296 = 0xD800, a UTF-16 surrogate (invalid Unicode scalar), so charFromCode
-- returns None → -1.  Proves the immediate reserved tag round-trips through `match`.
main = match charFromCode 55296
  Some c => charCode c
  None => 0 - 1
